   "source": [
    "The test set contains only 12 observations with 3 lapsed donors — individual test metrics are highly sensitive to which 3 donors landed in the test set. The 5-fold cross-validation results are the more reliable performance estimate and should be used as the primary evaluation reference."
   ]
